SOL A: Same as above, 51 earth pet TEARS through this dungeon with no problems at all even soloed the Lava Elemental room without even standing up.<br>
<br>
Runnyeye: FUN FUN FUN, 51 earth pet once again owns this.  I happened to travel downstairs near river and somehow (might ahve been bug) aggroed about 40 gobs which all decided to run at me while medding, all I can say is one cast of Scintalation, BOOM 40 dead gobs in one cast....<br>
<br>
Mistmoore: If done wisely MM can be taken piece o cake as well with 51 earth pet, he can knock through 4 at a time while i med np.  Soloed whole upper floor when i was trying for advisor robe way back when.<br>
<br>
Unrest: way way green once again, 51 pet can take out whole place alone.<br>
<br>
Crystal Caverns: First day velious opened I soloed way to Queen room and took camped her for 4 hours without dying.  Her room does have 7 spawns and if all 3 named are up in there no it cant be soloed by one mage.  But if all the PH are up there is a way to solo pull them all.  Orc section up top, just let pet go to town on every damn thing in site, its a joke..<br>
